 Nollywood star Belinda Effah has announced the official change of her name and she will now be known as Grace-Charis Bassey Effah. The actress shared the update in an Instagram post which read “I, formerly know as Belinda Uyu Effah, now wish to be known as Grace-Charis Bassey Effah. All former documents remain valid. General public please take note.” Captioning the post, now Grace-Charis wrote: Do You Still Need More Proof That’s It’s Me? My Surname is Still Effah. Thank You Very Much 🙏🏽
Yours Truly
